official_title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to extend the exclusion for employer-provided educational assistance to employer payments of qualified education loans.
short_title: Employer Participation in Repayment Act of 2019

summary.text:
Employer Participation in Repayment Act of 2019

This bill expands the tax exclusion for employer-provided educational assistance to include payments of qualified education loans by an employer to either an employee or a lender.
